===Etymology===
From "{{w|DirectX}} box". In use since the announcement of the original Xbox in 2000.
===Pronunciation===
* {{a|UK}} {{IPA|en|/ˈɛks bɒks/}}
===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
# {{lb|en|video games|trademark}} Any of the [[home console]]s in [[Microsoft]]'s ''Xbox'' product line, especially the original Xbox.
